ike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0477de4a50d72a4e64973b2016420fad628ef273","tid":595084,"uid":144401,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T01:08:25.000Z","msg":"啱啱開始玩 同樓主一樣見佢平先買<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T07:25:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個故事真係好正<br />\n打鬥又唔太複雜<br />\n有技能樹真係好正<br />\n仲有得啪啪啪(唔係重點）<br />\n今日得閒小小去搵曬成套貓派先"},{"pid":"a66a14cbfe998badb078daef0c0d4c8613f559ef","tid":595084,"uid":62318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-19T17:50:38.000Z","msg":"仲玩緊，玩到自己覺得好唔舒服<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個世界好真實，每個決定都有好壞處，每個角色背後都有故事，搞到我作為一個殺人滅口既主義者都殺到心理唔舒服<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n跟住我明明真係好鐘意Yen，但見到其他女巫向自己撒嬌果時又忍唔住想tum下佢地，做左好多背叛Yen既野，尤其是triss，明知yen唔鐘意佢，但我又唔想見到triss唔開心，跟住就<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n玩到自我感覺好差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但隻game真係好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49e92923548e92dece3a969d909e18b5fe2390bf","tid":595084,"uid":44460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T10:32:15.000Z","msg":"終於爆曬<br />\n爆完啲角色消失晒<br />\n得返yen, 冇得互動<br />\n好灰"},{"pid":"b495e79d634ad21919dbeda5d15fd186b1b96a83","tid":595084,"uid":7125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T15:42:56.000Z","msg":"你一周目都玩左個幾月，開二周啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d0b12e95d03c2a25784bd9380a96e09b815d21e","tid":595084,"uid":11185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T01:19:48.000Z","msg":"一路睇書一路玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /